snippet.textDisplay:
It was Mahashivratri of 2014. College mess mein mahashivratri mein bhaang milti hoti thi Mishrambu k sath.
Hum 6-8 logo ne sbne 3-4 glas pi hogi.
11:30-12 bje se kareeb sham ko 4 bje tk sbne ek room mein band hoke zameen mein bichhe hue bistaro pe baith k sirf piyush Mishra ko suna tha. What an experience it was!!
Husna k saath College k yaar aur bhaang mila do... it's beyond this world.
After all these years I'd say one of the most memorable experiences of my life and we created it out of nothing.
Those ups and downs that state of trans that bliss...still gives me goosebumps.

The place was Vivekananda Hostel, IIT BHU Varanasi.
What day what life!
